---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blogroll
description: Blogs and websites I read and recommend
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Blogroll
  order: 11
---

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h1>Blogroll</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">A curated list of blogs and websites I read regularly and highly recommend.</p>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    {%- for blog in blogroll.blogroll %}
    <article class="border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-amber-500 dark:hover:border-amber-500 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
        <a href="{{ blog.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-2xl font-semibold hover:text-amber-600 dark:hover:text-amber-400 flex items-center gap-2">
          {{ blog.name }}
          {% feather "external-link", class="w-5 h-5" %}
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">{{ blog.description }}</p>
      {%- if blog.tags %}
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {%- for tag in blog.tags %}
        <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 rounded">
          {{ tag }}
        </span>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
      {%- endif %}
    </article>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
      {% feather "rss", class="w-5 h-5" %}
      Want to add your blog?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      If you have a blog about web development, programming, or technology, feel free to 
      <a href="mailto:{{ metadata.author.email }}" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">reach out</a> 
      and I'd be happy to check it out!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
